description.en: The Energy Web Decentralized Operating System Open-Source Technology. The Energy Token (ENG) is a cryptocurrency belonging to the Energy Web Foundation (ENG). ENG Crypto providing Meta verse facility to buy/ sell property.  Using ENG's expertise and knowledge of environmentally friendly technology we are developing low cost, environmentally responsible energy solutions for powering large scale blockchain mining operations.
